# BD Bible Policy System - Cursor Rules

## Project Context
RPRC Business Development Bible Policy System for capture and proposal management.
Tech Stack: React, Node.js, Express
Styling: Inline styles with GMU brand colors ONLY

## CRITICAL BRAND REQUIREMENTS
USE ONLY GMU OFFICIAL COLORS:
- Primary Green: #006633
- Primary Gold: #FFCC33  
- Dark Green: #00563F
- Secondary Gold: #FFB81C
- White: #FFFFFF
- Light Gray: #F5F5F5

## Code Style
- Functional React components only
- Use hooks (useState, useEffect)
- Inline styles with style objects
- Optional chaining for safety: obj?.property || defaultValue

## Common Patterns
```javascript
// Import theme
import { gmuColors, gmuTheme } from './gmuTheme';

// Safe props
const Component = ({ documents = [], onNavigate }) => {
  // Always provide defaults
  const docCount = documents?.length || 0;
  
  // GMU styled button
  const buttonStyle = {
    backgroundColor: gmuColors.primaryGold,
    color: gmuColors.primaryGreen,
    fontWeight: 'bold'
  };
};
